lead_paragraph: Duke started the year as the nation's top-ranked team and Atlantic Coast Conference favorite. Yet as the start of league play arrives, little has gone to plan for the fifth-ranked Blue Devils.

headline.print_headline: No. 5 Duke Aiming to Get Settled, Develop as ACC Play Starts
